===Noun===
'''radius''' (''plural'' '''radii''')

#{{anatomy}} The long [[bone]] in the [[forearm]], on the side of the [[thumb]].
#{{geometry}} A line segment between any point on a the [[circumference]] of a [[circle]] and its center/centre.
#{{geometry}} The length of this line segment.

